These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, golf, badminton
1. the person who's sport is golf is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | lemonade | milk   |
| Sport      | swimming    | golf  | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, juice, almond-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, thai, french
1. the spanish is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the thai is on the far left##1
3. the thai is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | juice | water     | almond-milk      |
| Nationality   | thai | spanish | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, milk
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, strawberry, avocado
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | milk  | cola       |
| Food       | blueberry     | strawberry | avocado |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, cranberry, corn
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, baking
1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | corn    | cranberry     | raspberry |
| Hobby   | baking | drawing | traveling     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, hamster
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, train, tram
1. the person driving the train is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the owner of the pony is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | mouse | pony     | hamster |
| Transport   | tram        | skateboard | train    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, zucchini, papaya
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, quad-bike
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person eating papaya is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | papaya | banana      | zucchini  |
| Transport   | skateboard       | jet-ski | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, pop
3 different pets are kept: dog, snake, hamster
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of ambient is the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | d&b     | ambient    |
| Pet           | dog | hamster | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
