The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, drama, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | almond-milk    | juice    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | time-travel | thriller |

