The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, freelancer, manager
1. the freelancer is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating broccoli is in the middle##1
3. the fisherman is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | plum     | broccoli   | pineapple     |
| Job    | manager | freelancer | fisherman |

