.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, punk, dubstep
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | milk  | tea | coffee  |
| Music-Genre   | punk | dubstep   | ambient |

