.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, nectarine, broccoli
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, swimming, surfing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | broccoli | peas       | nectarine  |
| Sport   | surfing  | swimming | rowing |

 